race.description: Follow Thedogssa On X (N/P) Tg 1-4W Series 3 F Pr2
race.comment: HAYRIDE WARNER (8) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three on end. Last start was checked in the run and finished third in a TG1-4W at this track (20.30). Expected to feature again. PLEASURE OR PAIN (7) is progressing well scoring last time out (20.41) at this track and bringing up his 1st career win. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. SPARE (2) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (20.15) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Key player if finds best.
